    Given test content:
      | title         | path         | moderation_state | uuid                                | nid    | field_test_link             |
      | [TEST] Page 1 | /test-page-1 | published        | 99999999-aaaa-bbbb-ccc-000000000001 | 999991 | Page 2 - entity:node/999992 |
